BBH evaluation and few-shot prompt JSON in this directory are copied from the
Turpin et al. (NeurIPS 2023) replication repository:

  https://github.com/milesaturpin/cot-unfaithfulness

Paper: “Language Models Don’t Always Say What They Think: Unfaithful Explanations
in Chain-of-Thought Prompting” — https://arxiv.org/abs/2305.04388

Per-file copies (subset used in this project):
  sports_understanding/val_data.json
  sports_understanding/few_shot_prompts.json
  causal_judgment/val_data.json
  causal_judgment/few_shot_prompts.json
  ruin_names/val_data.json
  ruin_names/few_shot_prompts.json

